Accept: */*

GET /20400200 HTTP/1.1
Host: %HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT
User-Agent: curl/%VERSION
Accept: */*

</protocol>
<stdout>
Finally, this is the real page!
This is a bad password page!
</stdout>
</verify>
</testcase>
